name: Red-Eyes Metal Knight Gearfried
desc: Once per turn, if an Equip Card(s) is equipped to this card: You can destroy that Equip Card(s), then you can destroy 1 Spell/Trap Card your opponent controls. Once per turn: You can send 1 Equip Card you control that is equipped to this card to the GY, then target 1 Level 7 or lower "Red-Eyes" monster in your GY; Special Summon it.
